c: 2
v: 261
t: Isibonelo salabo sinjengesalabo abasebenzisa ingcebo yabo endleleni kaMvelinqangi kunjengo hlamvu (lombila) olumila izikhwebu eziyisikhombisa esikhwebwini ngasinye kumila ikhulu lezinhlamvu futhi uMvelinqangi uphindaphindela lowo omthandayo (izibusiso zakhe) futhi uMvelinqangi wazi kabanzi